members.name: RTCIdentityErrorEvent.idp
members.description: Is a DOMString describing the domain name of the identity provider (idp) generating the error response.

members.name: RTCIdentityErrorEvent.loginUrl
members.description: Is a DOMString giving the URL where the user can complete the authentication. It can be null and is provided by the identity provider (idp).

members.name: RTCIdentityErrorEvent.protocol
members.description: Is a DOMString describing the Idp protocol in use.
